Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Char and Sayla's encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...merely confirmed\Nhow far apart their beliefs were.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zanzibar destroyed\NWakkein's Magellan as it fled from Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the White Base returned to Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:02:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtype: Challia Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Until yesterday, Solomon had played\Nan important role...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the space strategy\Nof the Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it is serving as a base\Nfor the Earth Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the Federation has gained\Na vital foothold for its invasion of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon reinforcements would arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Federation Forces would launch\Na full-scale operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to be only a matter of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, a bizarre incident\Noccurred at Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it again! It says la, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Its course is E-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're there, you should see the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? We're not done fixing\Nthe electrical systems!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened? 38th Area! 38th Area!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah is causing\Nall those bursts of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I find it hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtype Lalah\Nand the mobile armor Elmeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're beyond all expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Something exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker! Where's the\Nenemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see it.\NThe Minovsky particle density is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like something's calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Put all crew members\Non anti-air surveillance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... There's something\Nvery strange around Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do feel\Na threatening presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Bright!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is ordered to\Nawait port entry at level 1 battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Deck 1 and Deck 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam, Guncannon, G-Fighter, take off!\NAll hands to level 1 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're working us to death here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Kikka!\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you guys bring me my normal suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sunmalo would get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla. I believe in you, but...\NDon't bring personal feelings into the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My actions thus fari\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just confirming, as your commander.\NI trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This Is G-Fighter!ff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is something the matter, Bright?\N- Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like Sayla is trying\Nto shoulder her troubles alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Guncannon taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a woman from Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Char's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural for him\Nnot to trust me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's... calling out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can almost... see something.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tired, Lalah?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain. But I'm fine.\NI can keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That'll be enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've accomplished plenty already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I hearing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure... something was calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A few hours before this incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gihren Zabi, Supreme Commander\Nof the Principality of Zeon's forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...was meeting with Lieutenant Challia Bull,\Nwho had just returned from Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that your fleet has returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...we need have no fear of a helium shortage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to allow this war\Nto continue for years to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd mentioned something about ending\Nthe war in one month, Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Challia Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be seated.\NLet's get to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the Newtypes you mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...I just have slightly sharper intuition\Nthan a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know more about you\Nthan you do yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered data showing your ability\Nas leader of the energy fleet to Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Flanagan Institute reviewed it.\NThe results are on the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Form of Newtype Development\Nin the Case of Challia Bull..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I have those abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You have abilities\Nyou haven't even noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's much about Newtypes\Nwe don't yet understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to put those abilities to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many people have died in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to serve under Lady Kycilia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. You knew it before I even said it.\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kycilia has been preparing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...a new mobile armor that will utilize\Nyour fighting readiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- As you wish, sir.\N- Good. The carrier Dolos is ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why\NI'm sending you to serve under Kycilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what your\Nunderlying intentions are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will make every effort\Nto understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be fine, Challia Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to read the minds of others\Nwill only lead to one's own downfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ask that you reflect on why\NI'm sending you to serve under Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the man named Challia Bull\Nis on this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! We'll have him operate\Nthe Braw Bro with Lieutenant Simus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If this Lt. Challia Bull's abilities\Nare greater than those of Lalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...we should consider\Ngiving him the Elmeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure Captain Char understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. I'll inform him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who has returned from Jupiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Newtype, he might be\Nmore promising than Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This console panel is surprisingly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Simus, I'm ready when you are.\NLet's launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that, Lt. Challia Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found out\Nwhat's making Lalah so tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The voltage used to register her brainwaves\Nhas a tendency to flow back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...which affects Lalah.\N- Can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to control the Elmeth's bits\Nfrom long range like we did today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do it.\NIt may even work to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder for her to confirm the enemy\Nfrom a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the psycommu does\Nenhance a person's intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be ready for combat again in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. If you get carried away in battle,\Nit could cost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the Braw Bro will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Come on. We'll go to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm a bit concerned about this Challia Bull.\N- Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not certain whether he'll consider\Nwhat's best for you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry\Nabout things like that, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Junior Grade Simus Bakharov\Nand Lt. Challia Bull...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...reporting for duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard. I'm Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ensign Lalah Sune,\Nthe Elmeth's pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Lalah,\Nthe Flanagan Institute's star pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I was just wondering\Nabout her lack of uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been asking the supply corps for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have her walking around the ship\Nlike this. It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Challia Bull...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. This young woman...\Nor rather, Ensign Lalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense something from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a kind of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What do you sense\Nfrom me, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I do like people like yourself, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could try to be more broadminded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I believe it would be of\Ngreat benefit to Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a piece of good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as if I've made a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the team, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. If we are in fact Newtypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm concerned about attaining peace\Nfor all Newtypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take that to mean\Nattaining peace for all humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. Do you understand\Nwhat the Lieutenant is saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Ensign Lalah has great powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Lt. Challia Bull...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...the pilot of the Gundam mobile suit\Nappears to be a Newtype as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the Federation has already\Ndeployed Newtypes in actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's certainly possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hayato! Are you allowed out of bed?\N- Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that the Gundam's control system\Nhas a tendency to overheat. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you dispatch the Lieutenant alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He insisted on testing the Braw Bro\Nand I couldn't dissuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You disapprove?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the Elmeth is adjusted\Nto suit you perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...I won't allow you to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to clear up your misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My misunderstandings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry with me, aren't you?\NI'm close to Char, and I hid that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Char is my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, how did you end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is... complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Are you going to leave the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base means too much to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...And when I think of my brother\Nbelieving that he can do the impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd give my life to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's warped my father's true ideals\Nand thinks he can achieve them himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my brother Casval anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that his real name? Casval?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... My brother... Casval...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the gold plates\Nmy brother gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please share them\Namong the White Base crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel better that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize how self-centered that must sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've chosen a difficult road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just treat you the same as I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...\NI can't help but admire your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I really doubt this is going to be as easy\Nas you think it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... I'll be counting on you, Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Possible enemy patrol ship detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Solomon requests that\Nwe launch interceptors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they going to make us do everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It proves that they trust us, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only as a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Order all units to take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gundam! Guncannon! G-Fighter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great, Ms. Sayla!\NI'll make up for the time I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just be observing for today,\Nuntil you get back on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there are three machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not Lalah. It's somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Challia Bull, enemy detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the fighting to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how much I can do,\Nbut please record all the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it! I'll give it my best try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy pilot can sense the direct line\Nbetween our position and Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different from the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Below!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it... The Gundam's reacting too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing mobile suit and pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot has to be a genuine Newtype.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, there's no way he could've\Nevaded the Braw Bro's all-range attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There are two or three mobile armors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back! This is unlike any\Nmobile armor we've seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kai! Where did it come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Kai! Where's the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back! This enemy is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's reacting too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot...!\NHe predicted I'd attack from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy should be just one mobile armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's overheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did he find us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Simus! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've pushed the Gundam\Nway past its breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's control system\Ncan't keep up with my speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If another enemy like that attacks,\Nwe'll be toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Challia Bull was defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I launch in the Elmeth right now,\NI can destroy the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate him, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation's already deploying\NNewtypes in battle, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundam pilot may not be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must try to avoid risks in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, the Gundam from Solomon\Nis too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We should think of Challia Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an unfortunate man,\Nwho knew that he was unable...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...to play right between\NLord Gihren and Lady Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting him die honorably was\Nthe best we could do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! You foresaw all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtypes are not omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they're just pathetic human\Nmutations spawned by war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No...! That can't be true...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the White Base crew\Nwas facing a grave situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fears about the Gundam's\Ncontrol system had become reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundam's system\Ncould no longer keep up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...with Amuro's ever-developing reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After a makeshift system is installed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundam departs\Nto follow the Revil fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahead of this fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...within Zeon's defense line...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...one brilliant mobile armor\Ndances gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NLalah's Dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah's Dilemma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:54.36,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:59.37,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:09.59,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:14.51,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.14,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:24.52,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:29.11,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:39.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:54.36,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:59.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:09.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:14.51,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.14,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:24.52,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:29.11,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:39.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
